(2, 64, 'Recursos Humanos', 'recursos-humanos', '<p>O nosso objetivo na gest&atilde;o de RH &eacute; atuar estrategicamente no planejamento, na organiza&ccedil;&atilde;o e no desenvolvimento, visando o engajamento das pessoas para o cumprimento eficiente e eficaz das atividades, potencializando o capital humano.</p>\r\n<p>Elaboramos folhas de pagamento, emiss&atilde;o e recolhimento de encargos sociais, recrutamento e sele&ccedil;&atilde;o, bem como todos os servi&ccedil;os pertinentes &agrave; rotina de pessoal.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 8, '2016-06-06 17:24:48', 558, '', '2016-06-13 22:19:07', 558, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-06 17:24:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"images\\/servicos\\/recursos-humanos.jpg\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"recursos humanos\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 3, 7, '', '', 1, 1393, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0, '*', ''),
(3, 65, 'Trabalhista e Previdenciário', 'trabalhista-e-previdenciario', '<p>Na gest&atilde;o de recursos humanos realizamos o acompanhamento trabalhista e previdenci&aacute;rio dos funcion&aacute;rios para que o condom&iacute;nio esteja completamente regular frente &agrave;s institui&ccedil;&otilde;es governamentais.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 8, '2016-06-06 17:25:35', 558, '', '2016-06-13 22:23:51', 558, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-06 17:25:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"images\\/servicos\\/trabalhista-previdenciario.jpg\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"trabalhista previdenciario\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 3, 6, '', '', 1, 1041, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0, '*', ''),
(4, 66, 'Contábil', 'contabil', '<p>Gerenciamos dados cont&aacute;beis do condom&iacute;nio tornando-os utiliz&aacute;veis tanto para finalidades internas, possibilitando tomada de decis&otilde;es, quanto para externas, como informa&ccedil;&otilde;es a bancos, governo e outros p&uacute;blicos. O controle gerencial dos n&uacute;meros oferece informa&ccedil;&otilde;es valiosas, apontando as diretrizes frente a qualquer tipo de mercado.</p>\r\n<p>Presta&ccedil;&otilde;es de contas mensais e anuais, atrav&eacute;s de balancetes e gr&aacute;ficos, confeccionados com a maior clareza para que todos os condom&iacute;nios possam entender de qual forma o sindico est&aacute; aplicando o dinheiro do condom&iacute;nio e suas necessidades.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 8, '2016-06-06 20:56:39', 558, '', '2016-06-28 12:49:59', 558, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-06 20:56:39', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"images\\/servicos\\/contabilidade.jpg\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"contabilidade\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 7, 4, '', '', 1, 1105, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0, '*', ''),
(5, 67, 'Financeiro', 'financeiro', '<p>Fazemos o controle mensal e o planejamento or&ccedil;ament&aacute;rio do condom&iacute;nio, verificando os indicativos do mercado financeiro externo e adequando-o &agrave; realidade. Nosso setor de contas a pagar realiza todo o controle das contas existentes no condom&iacute;nio e a quita&ccedil;&atilde;o das mesmas. Enviando para o setor cont&aacute;bil os comprovantes de toda a movimenta&ccedil;&atilde;o financeira, para que seja anexada ao balancete mensal.</p>', '', 1, 8, '2016-06-06 21:02:19', 558, '', '2016-06-28 12:50:39', 558, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-06 21:02:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"images\\/servicos\\/financeiro.jpg\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"financeiro\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 4, 5, '', '', 1, 1196, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0, '*', ''),
(6, 68, 'Tributário', 'tributario', '<p>Acompanhamos a aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o de encargos e tributos junto aos &oacute;rg&atilde;os fiscalizadores para que o condom&iacute;nio esteja cumprindo legalmente com seus deveres.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 8, '2016-06-06 21:51:47', 558, '', '2016-06-13 22:29:01', 558, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-06 21:51:47', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"images\\/servicos\\/tributacao.jpg\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"tributario\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 2, 3, '', '', 1, 991, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0, '*', ''),
(7, 69, 'Assessoria Jurídica e Cobrança', 'assessoria-juridica-e-cobranca', '<p>Disponibilizamos assessoria jur&iacute;dica preventiva, elabora&ccedil;&atilde;o, analise, revis&atilde;o e negocia&ccedil;&atilde;o de contratos, confec&ccedil;&atilde;o de notifica&ccedil;&otilde;es, editais e convoca&ccedil;&atilde;o de assembleias.</p>', '', 1, 8, '2016-06-06 23:26:53', 558, '', '2016-06-13 21:36:15', 558, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-06 23:26:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"images\\/servicos\\/assessoria-juridica-cobranca.jpg\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"assessoria juridica e cobranca\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 2, 2, '', '', 1, 1348, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0, '*', ''),
(8, 70, 'Novos Condomínios', 'novos-condominios', '<p>Sabemos que a conquista de um im&oacute;vel &eacute; a concretiza&ccedil;&atilde;o de um sonho e para a completa satisfa&ccedil;&atilde;o &eacute; essencial o aux&iacute;lio de profissionais competentes na implanta&ccedil;&atilde;o do condom&iacute;nio. Para isso, A Mais Brilho oferece bons servi&ccedil;os com as melhores condi&ccedil;&otilde;es do mercado, para o inicio de todas as rotinas, como:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Reuni&otilde;es de assembl&eacute;ias, elabora&ccedil;&otilde;es e registros das atas;</li>\r\n<li>Elabora&ccedil;&atilde;o da taxa de condom&iacute;nio junto aos cond&ocirc;minos;</li>\r\n<li>Contrata&ccedil;&atilde;o de empresas como fornecimento de g&aacute;s e seguro do pr&eacute;dio;</li>\r\n<li>Contrata&ccedil;&atilde;o de todos os funcion&aacute;rios do condom&iacute;nio.</li>\r\n</ul>', '', 1, 8, '2016-06-06 23:27:35', 558, '', '2016-06-28 12:54:06', 558, 572, '2017-05-16 15:57:32', '2016-06-06 23:27:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"images\\/servicos\\/novos-condominios.jpg\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"novos condominios\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 5, 1, '', '', 1, 1268, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0, '*', ''),
(9, 71, 'Conservadora', 'conservadora', '<p>Oferecemos servi&ccedil;os de limpeza e conserva&ccedil;&atilde;o para condom&iacute;nios residenciais, comerciais e empresa com um quadro de colaboradores e supervisores altamente qualificado e &aacute;gil para o r&aacute;pido atendimento das demandas, inclusive aquelas que necessitam de reposi&ccedil;&otilde;es imprevistas.</p>\r\n<p>Fazemos todas as previs&otilde;es de execus&otilde;es de servi&ccedil;os de:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Jardinagem;</li>\r\n<li>Limpeza caixa de gordura;</li>\r\n<li>Limpeza caixa d&rsquo;&aacute;gua;</li>\r\n<li>Limpeza de piso com ou sem jateamento.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Nosso trabalho &eacute; norteado por:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Metas operacionais alinhadas &agrave; necessidade de cada cliente;</li>\r\n<li>Avalia&ccedil;&atilde;o peri&oacute;dica das atividades, mapeadas por indicadores de desempenho;</li>\r\n<li>Avalia&ccedil;&atilde;o da satisfa&ccedil;&atilde;o dos clientes;</li>\r\n<li>Treinamento cont&iacute;nuo dos nossos colaboradores, visando sempre o aprimoramento das tarefas a serem desenvolvidas.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><img src=\"images/servicos/conservadora-mais-brilho.jpg\" alt=\"conservadora mais brilho\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" /></p>', '', 2, 8, '2016-06-06 23:28:33', 558, '', '2019-09-27 19:33:45', 577, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-06 23:28:33', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"images\\/servicos\\/conservadora.jpg\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"conservadora\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_c