(5, 1, 1, '', '2016-06-06 17:23:48', 558, 2493, '3dc70c2767ea402b7ede9b902250d21018fb9afb', '{\"id\":1,\"asset_id\":\"61\",\"title\":\"ADMINISTRA\\u00c7\\u00c3O\",\"alias\":\"administracao\",\"introtext\":\"<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Nossa prioridade \\u00e9 construir junto aos nossos clientes, s\\u00edndicos e cond\\u00f4minos, uma rela\\u00e7\\u00e3o de transpar\\u00eancia e confian\\u00e7a, oferecendo um atendimento diferenciado e personalizado aliado \\u00e0 gest\\u00e3o coparticipativa, onde todos t\\u00eam a possibilidade de criar, opinar e desenvolver solu\\u00e7\\u00f5es para a valoriza\\u00e7\\u00e3o e conforto do seu patrim\\u00f4nio. Al\\u00e9m da administra\\u00e7\\u00e3o do condom\\u00ednio, gerimos as necessidades dos nossos clientes, propondo in\\u00fameras solu\\u00e7\\u00f5es tais como suporte ao s\\u00edndico e ao corpo diretivo do condom\\u00ednio, an\\u00e1lise de demandas extracontratuais, visitas t\\u00e9cnicas regulares para acompanhamento e execu\\u00e7\\u00e3o de manuten\\u00e7\\u00f5es e outros.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"2\",\"created\":\"2013-11-16 00:00:00\",\"created_by\":\"558\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2016-06-06 17:23:48\",\"modified_by\":\"558\",\"checked_out\":\"558\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2016-06-06 17:22:52\",\"publish_up\":\"2013-11-16 00:00:00\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"sho