(48, 4, 1, '', '2016-06-28 12:49:59', 558, 2459, '4371930af9bfb97e8315a85945254185a33da998', '{\"id\":4,\"asset_id\":\"66\",\"title\":\"Cont\\u00e1bil\",\"alias\":\"contabil\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Gerenciamos dados cont&aacute;beis do condom&iacute;nio tornando-os utiliz&aacute;veis tanto para finalidades internas, possibilitando tomada de decis&otilde;es, quanto para externas, como informa&ccedil;&otilde;es a bancos, governo e outros p&uacute;blicos. O controle gerencial dos n&uacute;meros oferece informa&ccedil;&otilde;es valiosas, apontando as diretrizes frente a qualquer tipo de mercado.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Presta&ccedil;&otilde;es de contas mensais e anuais, atrav&eacute;s de balancetes e gr&aacute;ficos, confeccionados com a maior clareza para que todos os condom&iacute;nios possam entender de qual forma o sindico est&aacute; aplicando o dinheiro do condom&iacute;nio e suas necessidades.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"8\",\"created\":\"2016-06-06 20:56:39\",\"created_by\":\"558\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2016-06-28 12:49:59\",\"modified_by\":\"558\",\"checked_out\":\"558\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2016-06-28 12:49:23\",\"publish_up\":\"2016-06-06 20:56:39\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/servicos\\\\\\/contabilidade.jpg\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"contabilidade\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\"