t-size: 10.5pt; color: #003300; padding: 0cm; border: 1pt none windowtext;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\\">objetivo de &nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/samp><samp><span style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; color: #003300; padding: 0cm; border: 1pt none windowtext;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\\">trazer mais transpar&ecirc;ncia ao mercado de pagamento.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/samp><\\/p>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\\r\\n<p style=\\\"line-height: 16.8pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; color: #003300; padding: 0cm; border: 1pt none windowtext;\\\">Cronograma:&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\\"images\\/2.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"2\\\" style=\\\"float: right;\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><em><span style=\\\"font-size: 9pt; color: #003300;\\\">Junho de 2015 &ndash; Fim da oferta da cobran&ccedil;a sem registros para novos clientes;<\\/span><\\/em><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><em><span style=\\\"font-size: 9pt; color: #003300;\\\">Agosto de 2015 &ndash; In&iacute;cio da opera&ccedil;&atilde;o da base centralizadora de benef&iacute;cios;<\\/span><\\/em><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><em><span style=\\\"font-size: 9pt; color: #003300;\\\">Dezembro de 2016 &ndash; T&eacute;rmino da migra&ccedil;&atilde;o das carteiras de cobran&ccedil;a sem registro para a modalidade registrada;<\\/span><\\/em><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><em><span style=\\\"font-size: 9pt; color: #003300;\\\">Janeiro de 2017 &ndash; In&iacute;cio da opera&ccedil;&atilde;o da base centralizadora de t&iacute;tulos.<\\/span><\\/em><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size: 10pt;\\\">Para maiores informa&ccedil;&otilde;es acesse <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/portal.febraban.org.br\\/\\\">https:\\/\\/portal.febraban.org.br\\/<\\/a><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2016-12-26 10:26:17\",\"created_by\":\"572\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2016-12-29 20:13:40\",\"modified_by\":\"558\",\"checked_out\":\"558\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2016-12-29 20:12:27\",\"publish_up\":\"2016-12-26 10:26:03\",\"publish_down\":\"2017-01-26 10:26:05\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"right\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":13,\"ordering\":\"0\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"7\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\