(94, 9, 1, '', '2019-09-27 19:33:45', 577, 2964, 'bc1a1eb973d001eca2bcefad86c4d1e374a2e7fe', '{\"id\":9,\"asset_id\":\"71\",\"title\":\"Conservadora\",\"alias\":\"conservadora\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Oferecemos servi&ccedil;os de limpeza e conserva&ccedil;&atilde;o para condom&iacute;nios residenciais, comerciais e empresa com um quadro de colaboradores e supervisores altamente qualificado e &aacute;gil para o r&aacute;pido atendimento das demandas, inclusive aquelas que necessitam de reposi&ccedil;&otilde;es imprevistas.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Fazemos todas as previs&otilde;es de execus&otilde;es de servi&ccedil;os de:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Jardinagem;<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Limpeza caixa de gordura;<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Limpeza caixa d&rsquo;&aacute;gua;<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Limpeza de piso com ou sem jateamento.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>Nosso trabalho &eacute; norteado por:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Metas operacionais alinhadas &agrave; necessidade de cada cliente;<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Avalia&ccedil;&atilde;o peri&oacute;dica das atividades, mapeadas por indicadores de desempenho;<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Avalia&ccedil;&atilde;o da satisfa&ccedil;&atilde;o dos clientes;<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Treinamento cont&iacute;nuo dos nossos colaboradores, visando sempre o aprimoramento das tarefas a serem desenvolvidas.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\\"images\\/servicos\\/conservadora-mais-brilho.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"conservadora mais brilho\\\" style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" \\/><\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":2,\"catid\":\"8\",\"created\":\"2016-06-06 23:28:33\",\"created_by\":\"558\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2019-09-27 19:33:45\",\"modified_by\":\"577\",\"checked_out\":\"577\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2019-09-27 19:33:04\",\"publish_up\":\"2016-06-06 23:28:33\",\"publish_down\":\"\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/servicos\\\\\\/conservadora.jpg\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"conservadora\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":8,\"ordering\":\"0\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"1710\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0),
(95, 10, 1, '', '2019-09-27 20:24:45', 577, 2716, 'b0d09945da4d313f97f2203907fc2026fd1fb1a9', '{\"id\":10,\"asset_id\":\"72\",\"title\":\"A Mais Brilho\",\"alias\":\"a-mais-brilho\",\"introtext\":\"<p><img src=\\\"images\\/a-mais-brilho.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"a mais brilho\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px 0px 30px 30px; float: right;\\\" \\/>A MAIS BRILHO &eacute; uma administradora que busca atender todas as necessidades do condom&iacute;nio. Trabalhamos de forma intensa, para levarmos sempre as melhores solu&ccedil;&otilde;es e estrat&eacute;gias ao s&iacute;ndico.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Contamos com administradores de empresa; contadores, gestores em RH e graduados em Direito, ou seja, profissionais capacitados para conduzir todas as quest&otilde;es pertinentes a uma boa administra&ccedil;&atilde;o.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>A vasta experi&ecirc;ncia de seus s&oacute;cios que j&aacute; atuam na &aacute;rea revela o dom&iacute;nio de todo o processo da administra&ccedil;&atilde;o de um condom&iacute;nio com qualidade, profissionalismo e comprometimento.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Desta forma, apresentamos a seguir alguns dos servi&ccedil;os que executamos, firmando que nosso compromisso maior &eacute; atender e superar as necessidades e expectativas de nossos clientes.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"2\",\"created\":\"2016-06-07 00:10:16\",\"created_by\":\"558\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2019-09-27 20:24:45\",\"modified_by\":\"577\",\"checked_out\":\"577\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2019-09-27 20:24:19\",\"publish_up\":\"2016-06-07 00:10:16\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"